r":"#2-6","id":"1192060","time":"2016-11-28 19:23","userId":"fifth","userName":"fifth","userSign":"","message":"<div class=\"quote\"><q><span style=\"font-weight:bold;\">音月</span> 说: 准确来说是一起做，不是单纯给个任务做这样，例如android程序的图形和交互是我来做</q></div>~<br>虽然树莓派和arduino有点不一样不过基本原理都差不多，安卓开发不会但那之前的还是有所了解。<br>有问题可以问我能解答的可以解答，但是一起做还是算了"}]},{"avatar":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/user/m/000/00/96/9639.jpg","floor":"#3","id":"1192022","time":"2016-11-28 16:30","userId":"pimplemaster","userName":"ペロペロリン","userSign":"(关于我被绑架到Bangumi当不认真样本这件事 ... ...)","message":"树莓派做过类似的。<br>同样零基础，用得<a href=\"https://www.raspberryweather.com/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow external noopener\" class=\"l\">别人的轮子</a>给实验室弄了个温湿度计。<br>这个轮子是python+一点点C+Apache+Wordpress做的，测量温度湿度，发布到网站上。参照他的脚本，光感、土壤湿度、重量的传感器应该不难控制。浇水的机械结构最后落实到电磁阀挡板上也就是一句GPIO.HIGH/LOW。<br>还可以弄个树莓派摄像头，用openCV，在网页上实现实时图像监控。可以参考这个<a href=\"http://www.kscottz.com/open-skinner-box-pycon-2014/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow external noopener\" class=\"l\">自制树莓派斯金纳箱</a>的项目。<br><br>我不是理科生，也没有系统学过编程，从熟悉命令行到温度计上线三天打鱼两天晒网课余弄了也就一周。只要把板子线材传感器买好，学起来很快的。没有你想的那么难<img src=\"/img/smiles/tv/02.gif\" smileid=\"41\" alt=\"(bgm25)\">","sub":[{"avatar":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/user/m/000/18/11/181122.jpg","floor":"#3-1","id":"1192024","time":"2016-11-28 16:45","userId":"fifth","userName":"fifth","userSign":"","message":"我做的事情和你一毛一样，数据监控+拍照（不用浇水<br><span style=\"text-decoration: line-through;\">然而我自己写的轮子</span>"},{"avatar":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/user/m/000/00/96/9639.jpg","floor":"#3-2","id":"1192034","time":"2016-11-28 18:02","userId":"pimplemaster","userName":"ペロペロリン","userSign":"","message":"<div class=\"quote\"><q><span style=\"font-weight:bold;\">fifth</span> 说: 我做的事情和你一毛一样，数据监控+拍照（不用浇水<br>然而我自己写的轮子</q></div>厉害了！"},{"avatar":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/user/m/000/17/78/177820.jpg","floor":"#3-3","id":"1192336","time":"2016-11-30 08:16","userId":"franklinyu","userName":"Franklin Yu","userSign":"","message":"都有 Python 了為啥還要 Apache + Wordpress……"},{"avatar":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/user/m/000/00/96/9639.jpg","floor":"#3-4","id":"1192404","time":"2016-11-30 13:31","userId":"pimplemaster","userName":"ペロペロリン","userSign":"","message":"<div class=\"quote\"><q><span style=\"font-weight:bold;\">Franklin Yu</span> 说: 都有 Python 了為啥還要 Apache + Wordpress……</q></div>不知…也许造轮子的人觉得这样方便？"},{"avatar":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/user/m/000/18/11/181122.jpg","floor":"#3-5","id":"1193013","time":"2016-12-2 13:58","userId":"fifth","userName":"fifth","userSign":"","message":"<div class=\"quote\"><q><span style=\"font-weight:bold;\">Franklin Yu</span> 说: 都有 Python 了為啥還要 Apache + Wordpress……</q></div>可能造轮子的人刚学python"},{"avatar":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/user/m/000/00/96/9639.jpg","floor":"#3-6","id":"1193026","time":"2016-12-2 14:13","userId":"pimplemaster","userName":"ペロペロリン","userSign":"","message":"<div class=\"quote\"><q><span style=\"font-weight:bold;\">fifth</span> 说: 可能造轮子的人刚学python</q></div>跑回去看了一下，作者的说法是<div class=\"quote\"><q>here are other options that you can use instead of Apache, but I found it the easiest to set up because of Quick Cache.</q></div>"},{"avatar":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/user/m/000/17/78/177820.jpg","floor":"#3-7","id":"1193057","time":"2016-12-2 14:49","userId":"franklinyu","userName":"Franklin Yu","userSign":"","message":"<div class=\"quote\"><q><span style=\"font-weight:bold;\">ペロペロリン</span> 说: 跑回去看了一下，作者的说法是here are other options that you can use instead of Apache, but I found it the easiest ...</q></div>看到那行了，但是 Quick Cache 是啥插件…… <a href=\"https://wordpress.org/plugins/search.php?q=quick+cache\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow external noopener\" class=\"l\">沒搜到可能的結果</a>"},{"avatar":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/user/m/000/00/96/9639.jpg","floor":"#3-8","id":"1193227","time":"2016-12-2 23:35","userId":"pimplemaster","userName":"ペロペロリン","userSign":"","message":"<div class=\"quote\"><q><span style=\"font-weight:bold;\">Franklin Yu</span> 说: 看到那行了，但是 Quick Cache 是啥插件…… 沒搜到可能的結果</q></div>以前那个插件叫Quick Cache，现在好像叫Comet Cache"},{"avatar":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/user/m/000/17/78/177820.jpg","floor":"#3-9","id":"1193256","time":"2016-12-3 02:13","userId":"franklinyu","userName":"Franklin Yu","userSign":"","message":"<div class=\"quote\"><q><span style=\"font-weight:bold;\">ペロペロリン</span> 说: 以前那个插件叫Quick Cache，现在好像叫Comet Cache</q></div>原來如此，那就是<a href=\"https://wordpress.org/plugins/comet-cache/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow external noopener\" class=\"l\">這個</a>了。我懷疑作者自己也不是碼農，教程給我的感覺就是他更喜歡「鼠標點一點」，而不是命令行。網站（Wordpress）、服務器軟件（Apache）和 Python 腳本，在這教程裡面是分開配置的。如果是我的話，網站和腳本都用 Python，然後所有東西（包括 nginx 的配置腳本）都放在同一個代碼庫（repository）裡面，用戶 <div class=\"codeHighlight\"><pre>make install</pre></div> 一下就搞定了。（原來 BGM 的 code 標籤是 div.pre…… 好好的 code 不用 Orz）"}]},{"avatar":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/user/m/000/01/15/11503.jpg","floor":"#4","id":"1192027","time":"2016-11-28 17:26","userId":"moenayuki","userName":"名雪","userSign":"","message":"cc <a href=\"/user/calfn\" class=\"l\">@柳胜薰CALFN-触触小可爱VIP</a>","sub":[{"avatar":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/user/m/000/01/42/14268.jpg","floor":"#4-1","id":"1192247","time":"2016-11-29 21:14","userId":"calfn","userName":"触触✅个人认证","userSign":"","message":"联系，上了"}]},{"avatar":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/user/m/000/05/68/56836.jpg","floor":"#5","id":"1192028","time":"2016-11-28 17:27","userId":"maclauring","userName":"洗脸喵","userSign":"(兔子爱洗脸，我也爱洗脸。)","message":"Haha 不会","sub":[]},{"avatar":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/user/m/000/27/24/272459.jpg","floor":"#6","id":"1192030","time":"2016-11-28 17:31","userId":"272459","userName":"自动姬","userSign":"","message":"会，但是不在广州","sub":[]},{"avatar":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/user/m/000/00/34/3490.jpg","floor":"#7","id":"1192037","time":"2016-11-28 18:28","userId":"lhb5883","userName":"lhb5883-污🐱王VIP⑩","userSign":"(媛娇系是检验大法的唯一标准)","message":"毕业设计deadline：<br>上BGM✅<br>做毕设❌<br>流石bgm","sub":[]},{"avatar":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/user/m/000/01/05/10550.jpg","floor":"#8","id":"1192040","time":"2016-11-28 18:37","userId":"wioanfe","userName":"Kayano","userSign":"(保持自我怀疑，多思考)","message":"<span style=\"text-decoration: line-through;\">在广州，但已经几年没碰过Android了</span>","sub":[]},{"avatar":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/user/m/000/07/62/76206.jpg","floor":"#9","id":"1192041","time":"2016-11-28 18:40","userId":"explorare","userName":"YJSNPI","userSign":"(２４歳、学生です。)","message":"虽然是 Android 开发专业的，但我也要做毕设和实习，所以大概没什么时间搞这个。而且开发 Android 项目不是一两千能搞定的事，三五千买个毕设项目不如去找专业的买一整套包括论文。","sub":[{"avatar":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/user/m/000/14/14/141485.jpg","floor":"#9-1","id":"1192046","time":"2016-11-28 18:54","userId":"scarlet_feather","userName":"音月","userSign":"","message":"<img src=\"/img/smiles/tv/70.gif\" smileid=\"109\" alt=\"(bgm93)\">不是买个毕设项目，产品才是本体，android方面只是需要一两个界面而已，并不需要一个各方面完整可上市的成品，只是要能完成产品效果的展示和控制。"},{"avatar":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/user/m/000/07/62/76206.jpg","floor":"#9-2","id":"1192048","time":"2016-11-28 18:59","userId":"explorare","userName":"YJSNPI","userSign":"","message":"<div class=\"quote\"><q><span style=\"font-weight:bold;\">音月</span> 说: 不是买个毕设项目，产品才是本体，android方面只是需要一两个界面而已，并不需要一个各方面完整可上市的成品，只是要能完成产品效果的展示和控制。</q></div>那就很简单了啊，直接用 HTML5 开发就好了，三天上手。"},{"avatar":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/user/m/000/14/14/141485.jpg","floor":"#9-3","id":"1192049","time":"2016-11-28 19:02","userId":"scarlet_feather","userName":"音月","userSign":"","message":"<div class=\"quote\"><q><span style=\"font-weight:bold;\">Explorare</span> 说: 那就很简单了啊，直接用 HTML5 开发就好了，三天上手。</q></div><img src=\"/img/smiles/tv/39.gif\" smileid=\"78\" alt=\"(bgm62)\">在什么语言都不会的基础上也可以吗（不过之前真的没想到"},{"avatar":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/user/m/000/07/62/76206.jpg","floor":"#9-4","id":"1192050","time":"2016-11-28 19:05","userId":"explorare","userName":"YJSNPI","userSign":"","message":"<div class=\"quote\"><q><span style=\"font-weight:bold;\">音月</span> 说: 在什么语言都不会的基础上也可以吗</q></div>看你产品架构了。Web 伺服器那边得会 SQL，小项目就用 MariaDB 就行了，商业化得考虑 Oracle。然后是简单的 HTML5/CSS3 基础，现学现卖就好。基本不需要 Java 开发基础。别的就没了。想了想其实技术含量挺低的。不用考虑多线程，不用考虑内存优化。"},{"avatar":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/user/m/000/18/11/181122.jpg","floor":"#9-5","id":"1192056","time":"2016-11-28 19:21","userId":"fifth","userName":"fifth","userSign":"","message":"<div class=\"quote\"><q><s